race.comment: CRYPTONIC (3) deserves another chance after battling in the heavy (8) conditions with the 59.5kg second-up. Will relish the fast tempo and prove hard to stop from the good draw. Value contender. ALABAMA STATE (2) frustrating gelding on his final chance with J Mac aboard. Stalked the speed but lacked the dash when fourth to Alabama Fox over 1500m at Randwick in BM78 class. Look for him to swoop late. ATTRACTIVENESS (13) improving filly showing potential in her three career starts. Poorly weighted at latest with a fighting second over 1200m at Gosford in BM64 class. Gets the right run on the limit and has the upside to test some of these. DANISH PRINCE (6) tough gelding with a sound record over this course and distance. Will roll forward and will take catching with the 56.5kg. Each way. KYEEMA (9) bumped into a smart one second-up and gets another chance today. Can take a sit from the barrier and produce late.
